::KitKat::

She wondered through the forest and wondered where she was to go.
"Ok, occording to that thing in the lake, I'm a Predacon.  So now what?"
She kept walking and following her nose.  She picked up the scent of other 
bots.  Some smelled like that thing in the lake.  Some smelled kind of like 
her, in a way.  She kept walking untill she came to a bluff.  She looked 
down and saw bots talking.  One was a male and one was a female.  She 
glanced over and saw another bot in the trees. She crouched down and watched 
to see what would happen.  The one in the trees stepped on something that 
went snap.  The male talking to the female seamed to hear the snap.

She just stayed down, didn't move and watched under cover of some small 
bushes.
